Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:07.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}听我说啊 米赫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.46,0:00:12.82,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔他 贝尔他 搞外遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.71,0:00:16.91,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}可恶 说起来那个女孩算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.09,0:00:19.09,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔可是我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:23.31,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}喂喂 赫斯缇雅 贝尔可不是谁的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:25.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这点事我还是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:27.53,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}只是说说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:30.37,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}只是想说一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.17,0:00:43.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 求你了别从我面前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:46.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}喂喂 声音太大了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:51.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我爱你 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:33.01,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没事吧 神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.23,0:02:40.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神……神大人 怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:41.73,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:45.91,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}哼 什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:47.37,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔这个花心鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:50.41,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那个 神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:55.15,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这时候问有点抱歉 下次打工休息是什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:57.15,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}休息？怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:01.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}其实最近在地下城能挣到一点钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:04.29,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}所以对神大人想稍微报恩一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:05.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}所以那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:09.29,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}一起去吗 两个人去吃一顿好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:11.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:14.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}今天去吧 今天就想去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:15.57,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但……但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}今天就去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:19.29,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:20.73,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:29.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 6点西南的主街道 阿莫尔广场集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:40.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}和贝尔约会 和贝尔约会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:43.91,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}啊啦 赫斯缇雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:48.97,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}啊 得墨忒耳 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.25,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}还是一样的大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:55.99,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你不也很挺拔么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:58.31,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但是好吃惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:03.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你居然会来神殿浴场 不会是第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:08.59,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}其实一会有个约会 所以有点来干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.01,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}难道说……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:11.82,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对方是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:13.85,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那有什么关系么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:16.64,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}啊啦啊啦 赫斯缇雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}喂 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:20.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}赫斯缇雅居然有男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:23.77,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}在天界完全没有男人缘的赫斯缇雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.64,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}萝莉巨乳的赫斯缇雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:28.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对方是谁啊 老实交代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:32.21,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对方是我家族的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:33.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:39.13,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}啊 吵死了 我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:43.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}呐呐 赫斯缇雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:45.71,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你喜欢那孩子哪一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:47.31,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}全部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:02.71,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:09.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}抱歉 贝尔 让你久等了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:10.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:13.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我也刚到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:17.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}啊 那个就是传闻的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}赫斯缇雅的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:21.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:23.81,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:24.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:26.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:34.19,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}抱歉 赫斯缇雅 大家都很在意就跟过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}请放开我……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:40.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}啊啦 讨厌 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:46.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:52.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}赫斯缇雅逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:20.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}终……终于逃掉了 神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:24.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}真是的 所以才说神明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:26.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}一群沉沦于享乐的土狼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:29.11,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}都怪他们完全都夜深了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:32.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}难得的和贝尔的约会……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:34.41,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但是还是有点开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:36.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}而且 看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:38.89,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}请看 神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.37,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:55.17,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神大人 下次再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:57.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}下次一定请你吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:07.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我很期待哦 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:21.51,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}哦 比平常好一些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:25.13,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但是还完全不够啊 厄德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:30.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你这种不顶用的支援者能够成为我们苏摩眷族的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:32.33,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是多亏了谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:35.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}多亏了冒险者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:40.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你懂的吧 拼命的给我挣钱去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:46.82,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那家伙钱挺多的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.59,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不让他多挣点怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:53.59,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}什么冒险者大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:56.23,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:59.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}离目标金额还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:03.21,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那把短刀也一定要搞到手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:06.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}多亏了莉莉呢 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:12.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}真是奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:20.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}呐呐 你听说了吗 埃伊娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:25.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}苏摩眷族的冒险者又在换钱的时候发生争执了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:29.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是吗 为什么老是被逼成那个样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:36.19,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不知道 酒明明卖得非常好 应该不会是很缺钱的眷族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:47.61,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人 脚下！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:52.95,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不要！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:04.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}糟了 不小心用了魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:12.07,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人 没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:15.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}莉莉 谢谢了 帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:16.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:20.06,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}呐 莉莉 你刚才用了魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:23.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不 那是魔剑的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:28.15,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}魔剑？为了我用了那么贵重的东西？谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:32.75,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那是因为嘛 为了贝尔大人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:37.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}果然魔法好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:38.28,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}给
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:40.59,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}虽然是别人送的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:42.51,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:45.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那个 贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:49.85,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}明天我休息一天可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:52.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}可是可以 不过你有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:56.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}有眷族的集会 必须得出席
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:10:02.01,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我知道这是违反契约 我会支付罚金的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:04.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这种事就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:06.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}比起这个 对不起 莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:11.53,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是我想得不周到 想要休息的时候就直接说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}========
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:25.01,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:27.49,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}今天你休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:30.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是的 突然闲下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:32.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}希儿在休息日一般都干些啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:36.43,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这个嘛 读书之类的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:41.69,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}读书吗 但是神明大人的书好像都很难懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:45.75,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}哥布林也能懂的现代魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:47.53,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}有兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:52.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}虽然是客人落下的东西 但好像也没打算来取
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.63,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}如果这本书可以的话就借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:56.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:58.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}反正我也没啥损失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.77,0:11:01.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}看完了还回来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:05.89,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}魔法吗 好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:13.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}嗯 魔法有作为某些种族的素质而存在的先天系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:18.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}以及从神之恩惠中萌芽的后天系这两种
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:23.09,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}后天系的魔法就像是自我实现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:31.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对某种东西有兴趣 认同 憎恨 憧憬 叹息 崇拜 立誓 渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:34.99,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}契机总是存在于自己之中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:36.91,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那么开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:40.27,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对我来说魔法是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:46.89,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}强大的力量 烧尽弱小的自己 奋发向上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:49.71,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对我来说魔法是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:53.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}火焰 勇猛而炽热
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:57.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}一点也不适合弱小的自己的 红红的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:11:59.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我要向魔法寻求什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:05.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}想要追上像雷电一般比任何人都快的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:07.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}仅此而已？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:13.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}如果能够实现的话 想成为英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:17.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}就像以前读过的童话里的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:22.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}得到那个人的认同 成为英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:24.11,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}真是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:29.23,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对不起 但是 这就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:30.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这就是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:35.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:38.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:41.25,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神……神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:43.67,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}诶 啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:50.33,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}就是说 做了自己不习惯的读书 结果睡了个痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:52.01,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}好……好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:54.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:12:58.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神明大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:00.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:03.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}掌握了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:07.53,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神明大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:10.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}火焰箭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:14.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没想到居然能掌握魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.89,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这也是受那个技能的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:17.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神……神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:20.99,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}魔法 是魔法！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:23.95,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我会用魔法了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:34.73,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 你知道魔法是通过咏唱咒文来发动的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:41.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}通常咒文是在掌握魔法的同时与状态一同显示出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:48.19,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但是对于你 除了有“速攻魔法”的补充规则以外一个字都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:49.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:53.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这只是我的推测 你的魔法可能不需要咏唱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:14:00.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}嘛 总之明天去地下城试试就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:01.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:06.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没关系 不着急 你的魔法又不会跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:16.17,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对不起 神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:21.79,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我现在就想试试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.64,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}海带裹土豆 饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:31.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}刚出锅的赫菲斯托斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:43.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}火焰箭！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:50.27,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:54.13,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:55.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}火焰箭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:57.77,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}火焰箭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:14:59.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}火焰箭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:07.43,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}火焰箭 火焰箭……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:14.91,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}糟糕 都跑到了这个地方来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:17.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}得回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:21.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}回去了之后大家一定会吃惊的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:24.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}只身一人就打倒了阶层主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:46.65,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}精神疲惫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:50.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}看来是不顾后果的使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:51.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:54.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}什么 熟人么 艾丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:56.79,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}虽然没有直接说过话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:59.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那个 牛头人兽的时候的……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:04.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}原来如此 被我们的失误所卷入的少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:09.59,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}里维莉亚 我想补偿这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:15.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}现在对这个少年照我说的做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:18.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}作为补偿的话这就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:20.07,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那样就可以了么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:23.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}嗯 我就先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:36.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:40.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对不起 我不是你的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:42.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}幻觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:45.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}为什么总是要逃走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:14.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}又……又逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:17.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我这个笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:23.87,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}怎么了贝尔 做了噩梦了么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:28.55,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}难道是昨天读的这本书的错么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:33.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}魔导书？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:37.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没错 只要读了就能掌握与自身素质相适应的魔法的书
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:39.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}真真正正的魔导书
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:42.53,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这个到底是在哪里得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:47.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}在酒吧借的 说是别人忘记的东西读读看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:49.07,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}别人忘记的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:52.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}怎么了 神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:59.35,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 魔导书这个东西啊 只要看过一次就会失去效果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.23,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你打算去哪里啊贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:08.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}总而言之先道歉 然后再赔……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:09.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:12.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你知道魔导书值多少钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:18.73,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}赫菲斯托丝眷族的一等品装备的价值或者在那之上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:21.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}诶——
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:27.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}听好了贝尔 你没有看过这本书 就当这回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:29.61,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}后面的事我会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.75,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不行的啊 神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:39.17,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}别阻止我贝尔 下界有很多事花言巧语是解决不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:41.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}世界比神明还要随心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:45.15,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这种时候请不要说名言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:48.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对不起*4
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:52.13,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你还真做了很不得了的事情啊贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.39,0:18:56.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}等等……希儿为什么说的好像事不关己的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:18:59.99,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}果然不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:01.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}虽然很可爱但是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:04.87,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}蜜雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:06.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}忘了它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:07.21,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但……但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:09.19,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}看了就没有办法了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:12.25,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}把这东西丢在这里的人才不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:13.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但……但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:17.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我……我去迷宫了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:25.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那个……在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:31.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}哇 有了里维莉亚 苏摩那儿的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:33.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}呐呐 买了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:35.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}有什么不行啦 嘛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:36.99,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}谁是妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:41.89,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我是来补充道具的 不是来买酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:43.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}里维莉亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:46.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你是 埃伊娜么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:55.61,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对不起 里维莉亚大人 代替我买了那么贵的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.59,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}反正肯定是要买的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:20:01.79,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那么至少是为了你买的话 我心情也能舒畅些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:05.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}约定好了啊 要回答埃伊娜的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:10.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我知道了 那个关于苏摩眷族的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:12.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是的 请务必
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:18.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}嘛 总而言之让那边的孩子疯狂的不是苏摩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:20.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是酒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人已经来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:40.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}啊咧 莉莉还没有来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:43.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}啊 有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:47.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:48.75,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:52.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你……你是那个时候的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:56.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你和那小子混在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:59.17,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那么就不会什么都不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:01.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:02.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}别装呆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:03.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你来协助我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:06.11,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}一起灭了那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:11.87,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}别摆出那样的脸 你不是也惦记着那家伙存着的钱么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:18.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}同为冒险者 协力从不中用的搬运工那里搜刮个够吧 呐？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:21.01,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:24.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:27.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}切 这个混蛋小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.74,0:21:32.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:35.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}莉莉 什么时候在那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:40.01,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你和那个冒险者都说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:42.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不 都是无关紧要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:45.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}聊聊家常什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:50.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}话说回来莉莉你好像被纠缠上了 没有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:53.55,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是 没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.90,0:21:55.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:04.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}时机已到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,